# Слои бэкенда

Только бэкенд. BC-first на каждом слое.

## Дерево (текущее)

```
app/
├── Shared/ValueObject/           # EntityId, Phone, Email, Money
├── Domain/{BC}/
│   ├── Entity/ Enum/ ValueObject/
│   ├── Repository/               # interfaces (ports)
│   ├── Event/ Exception/         # где нужно
│   └── Service/                  # OrderFulfillment: OrderNumberGenerator
├── Application/{BC}/
│   ├── Command/ CommandHandler/
│   ├── Query/ QueryHandler/
│   ├── Presenter/ ReadModel/ Port/
│   └── Support/                  # OrderLoader, ClientLoader
├── Application/PublicSite/       # фасад bootstrap (без Domain)
├── Infrastructure/{BC}/
│   ├── Persistence/Eloquent|Mapper|Repository/
│   ├── Pdf/                      # OrderFulfillment: DomPdfRenderer
│   └── Auth/                     # ClientPortal, Identity (UserModel)
├── Infrastructure/Shared/Provider/PersistenceServiceProvider.php
├── Filament/
│   ├── Clusters/                 # 7 кластеров навигации /cp
│   ├── Resources/
│   └── Support/                  # OrderViewPresenter, Abstract*Resource
├── Http/Controllers/
│   ├── Api/                      # публичный REST
│   ├── Pos/                      # POS мастера
│   ├── Cp/                       # PDF из Filament
│   └── MainController.php        # SPA catch-all
└── Models/User.php               # алиас на UserModel
```

## Domain BC (7)

`OrderFulfillment`, `ClientPortal`, `Company`, `Pricing`, `Equipment`, `Warehouse`, `Identity`.

`PublicSite` — только Application-фасад (orchestration bootstrap).

Legacy `Domain/Catalog/` — не используется в runtime.

## Зависимости

Presentation → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure

## Статус

| Слой | Готово |
|------|--------|
| Domain + Infrastructure | да, по всем 7 BC |
| Application | да, включая Identity commands |
| Presentation | API + Filament `/cp` (7 кластеров) |
| Тесты | 25 (Unit Order + Feature по BC) |
